      "beta",
      "preview",
      "withdrawn"
    ],
    "description": "The stable cutline. A shiproom panel renders green for a Stable (or LTS) public claim only when its freshness packet is within SLO, every fitness function clears its threshold, every watched qualification row holds the cutline, any waiver it relies on is unexpired, an owner has signed off, and the public claim it backs is itself at or above the cutline; otherwise the panel narrows to beta, preview, or withdrawn."
  },
